  Compose `ColorFilter.tint(...)` or `Icon(tint = ...)`. Stroke width is
  2.0 / 48 viewport ≈ 4.17 % — deliberately *thinner* than the action
  icons (ic_receive / ic_send at 6.25 %) because this mark renders as
  the home-screen hero at 72–160 dp, where a 6.25 % stroke landed as
  a 4.5–10 dp absolute stroke and read as visually heavy.
-->
